DIRECTORY RELATED SYSTEM CALLS

Learn and apply in C Programs the following system calls (Directory related) 
· opendir(), closedir() 
· readdir_r(), readdir64_r() 
· lstat(), lstat64() 
·rewinddir() seekdir() 
· ftw(), ftw64(), telldir() 
· stat(), stat64() 
· dircntl(); dirent; dirent64; errno

SPOT EXERCISE

1. List all files and subdirectories that start with “ex” or “EX” for the user given directory name 

2. Demonstrate the difference between lstat() and fstat()
